      "file_path": "cps-application/src/main/resources/application.yml",
      "patchset_number": 1,
      "line": 55,
      "message": "not sure if changing this from the default is a good idea...\nThis is used by Hikari to help keeping connections alive...\nIt depends a lot on the postgres default behavior detecting 'idle' connections so the idea is to keep it alive and prevent Postgress taking back connections to quickly. In any case this will not effect our perforamcn while we are busy and have many threads using DB connections",
